			* #Set TWIKILAYOUTTOPIC = %TWIKIWEB%.TWikiLayout
			* #Set TWIKISTYLETOPIC = %TWIKIWEB%.TWikiStyle
		* CSS styling topics to be defined in local webs or in user topics (these can complement or override default TWiki style topics):
			* Set LAYOUTTOPIC = 
			* Set STYLETOPIC = 
		* Use the CSS TOPIC setting above to build the URLS used in the templates
			* #Set TWIKILAYOUTURL = %RELATIVETOPICPATH{%TWIKILAYOUTTOPIC%}%?skin=text&amp;contenttype=text/css
			* #Set TWIKISTYLEURL = %RELATIVETOPICPATH{%TWIKISTYLETOPIC%}%?skin=text&amp;contenttype=text/css
			* #Set USERLAYOUTURL = %RELATIVETOPICPATH{%USERLAYOUTTOPIC%}%?skin=text&amp;contenttype=text/css
			* #Set USERSTYLEURL = %RELATIVETOPICPATH{%USERSTYLETOPIC%}%?skin=text&amp;contenttype=text/css
